          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              Over 1000 students each year choose GradReady. In addition,
              = link_to "7 years in a row,", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score'), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
