              = link_to "student improved", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score'), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
              their score by
              = link_to "at least 20+ percentile points", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url(anchor: 'student_improved_score'), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
              after taking a GradReady course.
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              If you have any questions about any of our courses, please feel free to explore one of the options below or contact me through the
              = link_to "Contact Us", gamsat_preparation_courses_contact_url, style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
              page. Submitting a ticket through the Contact Us page will ensure that your query never gets lost.
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              Remember, for every friend you refer, your friend and you will
              = link_to "receive 10% and 5% percent off", faq_topic_url(type: 'gamsat', topic: 'enrolment-and-payment', anchor: 'refer_a_friend'), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
              respectively and
              = link_to "installment payment", faq_topic_url(type: 'gamsat', topic: 'enrolment-and-payment', anchor: 'Instalments'), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
              plans are available.
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              We look forward to you being one of our many
              = link_to "success stories.", gamsat_preparation_courses_student_testimonials_url, style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              If you're ready to start improving your GAMSAT results, please click 
              = link_to "here", "https://#{ENV['MAILER_HOST']}/gamsat-preparation-courses", style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;" 
              to explore your course options and their relative prices.

          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px;font-size: 15px;"}
              GradReady is a technology company that helps over 1,000 students each year through Adaptive Learning technologies - we make learning more engaging and efficient. Established in 2010 by medical students at the University of Melbourne, we have grown to operate in 5 cities nationwide.
